WEBVTT

00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:01.470 align:middle line:90%
[WHOOSH]

00:00:01.470 --> 00:00:09.310 align:middle line:90%


00:00:09.310 --> 00:00:11.270 align:middle line:90%
[MUSIC PLAYING]

00:00:11.270 --> 00:00:16.690 align:middle line:90%


00:00:16.690 --> 00:00:21.100 align:middle line:84%
>> The minute you start to
allow yourself to be beautiful,

00:00:21.100 --> 00:00:27.430 align:middle line:84%
the minute you can say not I
would be fine if I were this

00:00:27.430 --> 00:00:34.460 align:middle line:90%
way, but I am, I am.

00:00:34.460 --> 00:00:37.790 align:middle line:84%
Close your eyes and say
to yourself now, I am.

00:00:37.790 --> 00:00:40.970 align:middle line:90%


00:00:40.970 --> 00:00:44.930 align:middle line:84%
And look at all your
stuff and just let it be.

00:00:44.930 --> 00:00:48.440 align:middle line:84%
Don't wish it any other way
than it is, and just say

00:00:48.440 --> 00:00:55.100 align:middle line:84%
I am and allow your personality,
all your problems, your body

00:00:55.100 --> 00:00:58.970 align:middle line:84%
and all its problems, your
social scene and economic scene

00:00:58.970 --> 00:01:03.170 align:middle line:84%
and all its problems, see it all
as just the workings of nature,

00:01:03.170 --> 00:01:08.815 align:middle line:84%
like trees grow and trees die
and rivers and fish and brooks

00:01:08.815 --> 00:01:10.610 align:middle line:90%
and all of it.

00:01:10.610 --> 00:01:13.940 align:middle line:84%
Just look at it all
and allow it space,

00:01:13.940 --> 00:01:19.660 align:middle line:84%
and see that within
it all, I am.

00:01:19.660 --> 00:01:21.880 align:middle line:90%
I am.

00:01:21.880 --> 00:01:24.870 align:middle line:90%
I am.

00:01:24.870 --> 00:01:30.060 align:middle line:84%
And as more and more you
begin to recognize the I

00:01:30.060 --> 00:01:35.460 align:middle line:84%
am, when you look
at other beings,

00:01:35.460 --> 00:01:38.190 align:middle line:90%
you will see that in them.

00:01:38.190 --> 00:01:44.160 align:middle line:90%
An I am meets I am in love--

00:01:44.160 --> 00:01:48.780 align:middle line:84%
not romantic love, not
possessive love, not

00:01:48.780 --> 00:01:54.270 align:middle line:84%
needful love, not jealous
love, not the polarity

00:01:54.270 --> 00:02:02.010 align:middle line:84%
of love and hate in the ocean of
love, because you can add on I

00:02:02.010 --> 00:02:04.510 align:middle line:90%
am love.

00:02:04.510 --> 00:02:06.570 align:middle line:90%
I am love.

00:02:06.570 --> 00:02:09.580 align:middle line:90%


00:02:09.580 --> 00:02:14.420 align:middle line:84%
I'm not asking you what your
emotions are at this moment.

00:02:14.420 --> 00:02:16.990 align:middle line:90%
I am love.

00:02:16.990 --> 00:02:19.840 align:middle line:90%


00:02:19.840 --> 00:02:22.500 align:middle line:90%
I am awareness.

00:02:22.500 --> 00:02:25.780 align:middle line:90%


00:02:25.780 --> 00:02:28.735 align:middle line:90%
I am energy.

00:02:28.735 --> 00:02:31.420 align:middle line:90%


00:02:31.420 --> 00:02:36.010 align:middle line:84%
Feel your whole body as merely
a pulsating pattern of energy,

00:02:36.010 --> 00:02:39.290 align:middle line:84%
all of your thoughts
as forms of energy.

00:02:39.290 --> 00:02:43.060 align:middle line:84%
See it all as just patterns
and patterns of energy.

00:02:43.060 --> 00:02:49.220 align:middle line:90%
I am the spirit made manifest.

00:02:49.220 --> 00:02:54.160 align:middle line:90%
I am the spirit made manifest.

00:02:54.160 --> 00:03:02.760 align:middle line:90%
I am what I am and I am God.

00:03:02.760 --> 00:03:06.100 align:middle line:84%
All of the difficulties
with your body,

00:03:06.100 --> 00:03:10.140 align:middle line:84%
all of the difficulties
in your social world,

00:03:10.140 --> 00:03:13.830 align:middle line:84%
all of the difficulties
in your personality,

00:03:13.830 --> 00:03:20.610 align:middle line:84%
all will fall into perspective
as you recognize I am.

00:03:20.610 --> 00:03:23.250 align:middle line:84%
Some of them will disappear,
because you won't need them

00:03:23.250 --> 00:03:24.880 align:middle line:90%
anymore.

00:03:24.880 --> 00:03:27.030 align:middle line:84%
And some of them
you will understand

00:03:27.030 --> 00:03:31.680 align:middle line:84%
as the perfect expression of
the working out of your karma,

00:03:31.680 --> 00:03:34.840 align:middle line:84%
and you will allow
them to continue.

00:03:34.840 --> 00:03:36.600 align:middle line:90%
Make sure you heard that.

00:03:36.600 --> 00:03:40.350 align:middle line:84%
When you have entered
into the place of I

00:03:40.350 --> 00:03:45.840 align:middle line:84%
am, then all of your
physical problems,

00:03:45.840 --> 00:03:53.100 align:middle line:84%
all of your social problems, all
of your psychological problems

00:03:53.100 --> 00:03:56.340 align:middle line:90%
will come into perspective.

00:03:56.340 --> 00:04:02.570 align:middle line:84%
Those that you do not
need will fall away.

00:04:02.570 --> 00:04:09.990 align:middle line:84%
Others you will recognize
as the perfect working out

00:04:09.990 --> 00:04:16.470 align:middle line:84%
of your karma, and you will
allow them to continue.

00:04:16.470 --> 00:04:17.720 align:middle line:90%
I am love.

00:04:17.720 --> 00:04:22.320 align:middle line:90%


00:04:22.320 --> 00:04:25.440 align:middle line:90%
Who I am is not vulnerable.

00:04:25.440 --> 00:04:28.070 align:middle line:90%


00:04:28.070 --> 00:04:36.780 align:middle line:84%
When your body dies,
I am before time.

00:04:36.780 --> 00:04:40.040 align:middle line:90%
I am.

00:04:40.040 --> 00:04:44.450 align:middle line:84%
With each problem
you think you have,

00:04:44.450 --> 00:04:48.890 align:middle line:84%
see that it is your model
of having the problem that

00:04:48.890 --> 00:04:50.870 align:middle line:90%
is the problem.

00:04:50.870 --> 00:04:54.080 align:middle line:84%
Don't analyze your
way out of it.

00:04:54.080 --> 00:04:59.640 align:middle line:84%
Just sit down quietly
and follow your breath.

00:04:59.640 --> 00:05:03.650 align:middle line:84%
And if you can learn
how to talk to God

00:05:03.650 --> 00:05:08.060 align:middle line:84%
or talk to your inner
guru, open your heart.

00:05:08.060 --> 00:05:12.380 align:middle line:84%
Be in an intimate relationship
with your beloved.

00:05:12.380 --> 00:05:14.900 align:middle line:90%
Talk through the Divine Mother.

00:05:14.900 --> 00:05:19.040 align:middle line:84%
Be in love with
the spirit of God.

00:05:19.040 --> 00:05:22.950 align:middle line:84%
Open your heart in
the inner chambers

00:05:22.950 --> 00:05:27.050 align:middle line:84%
and say to your beloved,
let me know you.

00:05:27.050 --> 00:05:29.810 align:middle line:90%
Let me merge into you.

00:05:29.810 --> 00:05:34.580 align:middle line:84%
Let me even pass by my
separateness of my love

00:05:34.580 --> 00:05:38.180 align:middle line:90%
for you to become one with you.

00:05:38.180 --> 00:05:40.250 align:middle line:90%
That's the prayer.

00:05:40.250 --> 00:05:44.450 align:middle line:84%
When you pray to God, pray for
God, that's the route home.

00:05:44.450 --> 00:05:45.250 align:middle line:90%
It's all said.

00:05:45.250 --> 00:05:46.610 align:middle line:90%
It's right there.

00:05:46.610 --> 00:05:48.710 align:middle line:90%
It's in every motel room.

00:05:48.710 --> 00:05:51.065 align:middle line:84%
The living truth, everything
you needed to know

00:05:51.065 --> 00:05:54.580 align:middle line:84%
is sitting right
there, right there.

00:05:54.580 --> 00:06:02.000 align:middle line:90%